      ],
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "Narrator", "text": "She lies motionless for a moment longer, hoping the ache will pass..." },
        { "speaker": "Narrator", "text": "But it only grows worse. Sharp. Stubborn." },
        { "speaker": "Narrator", "text": "With a groan, she forces herself up and drags her feet toward the dresser." },
